column2: This makes me sick to my stomach. Because this bitch new that she could get away with it because she’s a woman and he’s a man. I as a teenage female am disgusted by her and I am on Johnny Depps side!

column2: Not only is Amber Heard a shameless liar and a phony, her actions are a disgrace to any woman who has ACTUALLY suffered domestic violence and been brave enough to come forward. I'm not suggesting that she never be allowed to work in the industry again; I find 'cancel' culture abhorrent. What I am suggesting is that she be held accountable for her actions, like every adult should be. Until Hollywood comes to it's senses collectively, and allows Johnny Depp the option to resume the roles he's been denied due to Amber Heard's slander, I will be boycotting any entity that supports or endorses her, as well as any entity that refuses to allow Johnny Depp to resume his work. I'll be urging all those I know to do likewise.

column2: Amber Heard has a history of being abusive emotionally  and physically to not only Johnny Depp but other partners and employees. She was even arrested for domestic violence by an officer who witness the assault. Heard should not be rewarded for accusing someone else of the very crimes she herself has perpetrated onto others. Johnny Depp who did not have this history in his former relationships is the victim of abuse and at some point victims do fight back as a result of the abuse. He should not be punished for being a victim. I for one will not watch Aquaman 2 if she is in it and I am sure I am not alone.

column2:
Given that:

 

1) Suicide is a leading cause of death in men

2) Divorce is a leading cause of male suicide

3) Amber Heard just filed for divorce against Johnny Depp

4) Her petition for divorce was just filed days after the death of his mother, which is one of the times in a man's life when he will be at his lowest point and needs all the support that he can get

5) Through her action in filing for divorce, Amber has shown herself to be an absolutely contemptible human being completely devoid of any compassion for anyone other than herself

 

We, the undersigned, have chosen to stand in solidarity with Mr. Depp and swear for the rest of our lives to boycott anything and everything that has been in any way touched by Amber Heard including any and all media she is involved with, including, but not limited to, her movies, TV shows, music, books, blogs, etc., past, present and future, as well as any charities she is involved with now or in the future, regardless of our own personal feelings for said charities, so long as she is a spokesperson. Even if she changes her mind later on, perhaps because of this petition, we, the undersigned, will not.
